          %p
            Frameworks and tools focused on the agile development, such as:
            %ul
              %li Ruby
              %li AngularJS
              %li Bootstrap
              %li etc.
      .content
        %h2.content-head.is-center Know more about Us.
        .pure-g
          .l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-md-2-5
            %form.pure-form.pure-form-stacked
              %fieldset
                %legend Leave your message
                %label{:for => "name"} Your Name
                %input#name{:placeholder => "Your Name", :type => "text"}
                  %label{:for => "email"} Your Email
                  %input#email{:placeholder => "Your Email", :type => "email"}
                    %label{:for => "message"} Your Message
                    %textarea#message{:cols => "50", :placeholder => "Your Message", :rows => "5"}
                    %button.pure-button{:type => "submit"}
                      %i.fa.fa-send
                      Send Message
          .l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-md-3-5
            %h4 We are
            .l-box-lrg.pure-u-1
              .hexagon
                %a{href: 'https://twitter.com/learod87', target: '_blank'}
                  %span
                    %i.fa.fa-twitter
                %a{href: 'https://github.com/learod', target: '_blank'}
                  %span
                    %i.fa.fa-github
                Leandro
                .face1
                .face2
            .l-box-lrg.pure-u-1
              .css-shapes-preview
            %h4 More Information
            %p
              We are located at Corrientes, ARG.
